On Tue, Feb 3, 2026 at 8:25 PM Yoav Weiss (@Shopify) &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="453c2a243332206b6b6b05262d372a282c30286b2a3722"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
