&gt;&gt; On Fri, Dec 19, 2025 at 2:52 PM Reilly Grant &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="ff8d9a9693d1d1d1bf9c978d9092968a92d1908d98"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
