&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Throwaway peerconnections are an antipattern too ;-)
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Since RTCConfiguration is not exposed on window one can not 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; feature detect upfront but one can call pc.getConfiguration() to 
